messages.message: Hello team. From the roadmap, I remember we're working on a detailed report of consumption per workspace, project and user, if I'm not wrong. Do we also have plans to limit the consumption (pre-paid Units) per project, workspace, user/group? Our new client, Fleury, asked us if we could do that without having to have separate accounts for each project.
The first version of this will just be tracking. We don't currently have plans to add limiting.
